	  Apply a gaussian blurr to an image
</description>
  <version>0.1.0.$Revision: 1.1 $(alpha)</version>
  <documentation-url>http://www.slicer.org/slicerWiki/index.php/Modules:GaussianBlur-Documentation-3.6</documentation-url>
